12. Summary

This design introduces a validation framework that verifies ArcOS image integrity and correctness after installation and upgrade workflows.

The solution ensures that only approved ArcOS images are accepted by validating:

- software version
- image fingerprint
- checksum integrity

before marking installation or upgrade workflows successful.
